OL,3,CWhy Summerland remains the forgotten
OL,4,Cdisaster and how it should be
OL,5,Cremembered
OL,7,FMeanwhile, the majority of people in
OL,8,Fthe UK were unfamiliar with Summerland
OL,9,Fas a leisure complex, let alone the
OL,10,Fdisaster that unfolded.
OL,12,FThat was until one survivor took the
OL,13,Fbrave decision to speak publicly about
OL,14,Fher trauma for the first time on
OL,15,Fcamera.
OL,17,FJackie Hallam was holidaying in the
OL,18,FIsle of Man with her mum Lorna, and
OL,19,Fbest friend Jane.
