OL,3,CWhy Summerland remains the forgotten
OL,4,Cdisaster and how it should be
OL,5,Cremembered
OL,7,FOn that fateful night in 1973, the
OL,8,Ftrio were inside Summerland as the
OL,9,Ffire ripped through the complex.
OL,11,FBoth Lorna and Jane died in the blaze.
OL,13,FJackie escaped with severe burns, and
OL,14,Fa trauma that would last a lifetime.
OL,16,FLast year, Jackie faced her trauma
OL,17,Fonce more - returning to the Isle of
OL,18,FMan and revisiting the Summerland site
OL,19,Ffor the first time in 50 years.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
