OL,3,CWhy Summerland remains the forgotten
OL,4,Cdisaster and how it should be
OL,5,Cremembered
OL,7,FAnd it is that sense of injustice that
OL,8,Fis also felt by the 'Justice for
OL,9,FSummerland' campaigners today.
OL,11,FBecause while the Chief Minister of
OL,12,Fthe Isle of Man did make a historic
OL,13,Fapology for any governance failings,
OL,14,Fhe has not committed to looking into
OL,15,Fthe 'death by misadventure' verdicts.
OL,17,FBut this story appears far from over.
